would depend on x.

01:15:01.010 --> 01:15:07.100
But if we assume that
the system is uniform,

01:15:07.100 --> 01:15:10.150
then we can drop that force.

01:15:13.990 --> 01:15:25.720
So to be precise, let's do this
for the case of five 0 field.

01:15:25.720 --> 01:15:29.620
Because when you are at
zero field in a magnet,

01:15:29.620 --> 01:15:33.420
