space are all the same to you.

01:15:33.420 --> 01:15:36.230
There's no reason to be pointing
one direction as opposed

01:15:36.230 --> 01:15:38.060
to another direction.

01:15:38.060 --> 01:15:50.730
So because of this symmetry in
rotations, in this function,

01:15:50.730 --> 01:15:54.420
you cannot have M-- actually,
