01:15:54.420 --> 01:15:55.290
reasons.

01:15:55.290 --> 01:15:57.020
Well, OK.

01:15:57.020 --> 01:16:00.170
You couldn't have M because it
would break the directionality.

01:16:03.780 --> 01:16:07.640
But you could have
something that is M squared.

01:16:07.640 --> 01:16:13.815
Again, to be precise, M
