01:17:16.340 --> 01:17:18.780
Mute and so forth--
so there's all kinds

01:17:18.780 --> 01:17:21.990
of terms such as that can
be appearing in this series.

01:17:21.990 --> 01:17:26.400
Gradients-- there's a term
