01:22:06.490 --> 01:22:10.050
Let's get here a T over 2.

01:22:10.050 --> 01:22:11.840
There will be
higher order terms.

01:22:11.840 --> 01:22:13.580
There will be M to the fourth.

01:22:13.580 --> 01:22:15.046
There will be M to the sixth.

01:22:15.046 --> 01:22:17.170
There will be a whole bunch
