01:22:22.280 --> 01:22:27.079
So there will be K over
2, gradient of M squared.

01:22:27.079 --> 01:22:31.160
There will be L over 2
Laplacian of M squared.

01:22:31.160 --> 01:22:33.600
There would be higher
